This tool use to build pld load entry.

in host compile env
1. put the pld_tool same dir with rom, fsbl, u-boot-2021.10, ramdisk, etc.
2. after build bl1, bl2, bl31, u-boot.bin, Image and boot.cpio.gz.img,
    run:
        pushd pld_tool
        ./compile.sh
    then cp pld_backdoor_realddr.tgz to pld server.

in pld server
1. in pld server work dir, run tar -zxvf pld_backdoor_realddr.tgz.
2. cp script/*.tcl your_workdir/script/
3. cp c_build/*.h your_ workdir/c_build
if want to update bl1.bin.text, should cp bl1.bin.text to c_build dir in pld server.

